  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/803e0a6800c6c9226f86d6d4640fdd53.gif?t=1753153665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/803e0a6800c6c9226f86d6d4640fdd53.poster.avif?t=1753153665\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your arch nemesis has taken your invention called the Dimension Jumper! This device lets its user travel to any dimension they wish! Except your arch nemesis has used it to send you into a place known as Cosmic Parkour! A land filled with terrain and entity-based dangers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/26d075981ab978b4f9cbfdbd02a6e226.poster.avif?t=1753153665\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/26d075981ab978b4f9cbfdbd02a6e226.webm?t=1753153665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/26d075981ab978b4f9cbfdbd02a6e226.mp4?t=1753153665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 40 levels for you to complete! Which includes boss fights and bonus levels!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use hints, problem solving skills and awesome parkour to complete each level!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More levels are added with game updates!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* Originally released to the Microsoft Store in 2023 for Windows 10/11 and Xbox.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/803e0a6800c6c9226f86d6d4640fdd53.gif?t=1753153665\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/803e0a6800c6c9226f86d6d4640fdd53.poster.avif?t=1753153665\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your arch nemesis has taken your invention called the Dimension Jumper! This device lets its user travel to any dimension they wish! Except your arch nemesis has used it to send you into a place known as Cosmic Parkour! A land filled with terrain and entity-based dangers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/26d075981ab978b4f9cbfdbd02a6e226.poster.avif?t=1753153665\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/26d075981ab978b4f9cbfdbd02a6e226.webm?t=1753153665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028900/extras/26d075981ab978b4f9cbfdbd02a6e226.mp4?t=1753153665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are over 40 levels for you to complete! Which includes boss fights and bonus levels!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use hints, problem solving skills and awesome parkour to complete each level!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More levels are added with game updates!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>* Originally released to the Microsoft Store in 2023 for Windows 10/11 and Xbox.</i></p>",
